HEADWORD: Hesperidium
<hw>Hes`pe*rid"i*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. So
called in allusion to the golden apples of the Hesperides. See
<er>Hesperides</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A large berry with a
